      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Studying Both Dictionaries</h2>
      <p>Serious competitive players often learn both word lists. The overlap between TWL and SOWPODS is enormous — over 98% of words appear in both. The practical approach is to master the shared core, then learn the exclusives for whichever context you play in most.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
