          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Start with TWL:</span> If you play primarily in North America, learn TWL thoroughly first. Every TWL word is also valid in SOWPODS (with very rare exceptions).</p>
        </div>
